note20 = Note.create(user_id: 1, notebook_id: 4, title: "Dubai", body: "<p>Dubai is a city in the United Arab Emirates known for luxury shopping, ultramodern architecture and a lively nightlife scene. Burj Khalifa, an 830m-tall tower, dominates the skyscraper-filled skyline. At its foot lies Dubai Fountain, with jets and lights choreographed to music. On man-made islands just offshore is Atlantis, the Palm, a resort with water and marine-animal parks.</p><p></p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?biw=1920&amp;bih=985&amp;q=dubai+getting+there&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiLmYHTmK7LAhVL3GMKHdrRAq0Q6BMIlwEoADAa\"><strong>Getting there</strong></a><strong>: </strong>15 h 45 min flight</p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?biw=1920&amp;bih=985&amp;q=dubai+population&amp;stick=H4sIAAAAAAAAAOPgE-LUz9U3MEwzsCjS0spOttLPyU9OLMnMz9MvLgHSxSWZyYk58UWp6UAhq4L8gtIcsCwAbHZ2ZjkAAAA&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiLmYHTmK7LAhVL3GMKHdrRAq0Q6BMIngEoADAc\"><strong>Population</strong></a><strong>: </strong>2.459 million (Jan 29, 2016)</p></li></ul><p></p><p><img src=\"http://res.cloudinary.com/dlvkhiu0c/image/upload/v1457340542/a70ebfc3a84c4e7affff25c950869ad0_ite9ky.jpg\" alt=\"Dubai\" title=\"Dubai\"></p>")

note21 = Note.create(user_id: 1, notebook_id: 4, title: "Phuket", body: "<p>Phuket, a rainforested, mountainous island in the Andaman Sea, has some of Thailand’s most popular beaches, mostly situated along the clear waters of the western shore. The island is home to many high-end seaside resorts, spas and restaurants. Patong, the main town, has a more casual vibe and is filled with wild nightclubs, bars and discos.</p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?biw=1920&amp;bih=985&amp;q=phuket+area&amp;stick=H4sIAAAAAAAAAOPgE-LUz9U3MMxKMk_XkspOttLPyU9OLMnMz4MzrBKLUhMB02VR0CkAAAA&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjQxY6Dma7LAhUBV2MKHdPEBmAQ6BMIkgEoADAU\"><strong>Area</strong></a><strong>: </strong>209.7 mi²</p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?biw=1920&amp;bih=985&amp;q=phuket+elevation&amp;stick=H4sIAAAAAAAAAOPgE-LUz9U3MMxKMk_Xks9OttLPyU9OLMnMz4MzrFJzUsvALAAlifENLgAAAA&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjQxY6Dma7LAhUBV2MKHdPEBmAQ6BMIlQEoADAV\"><strong>Elevation</strong></a><strong>: </strong>1,736′</p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?biw=1920&amp;bih=985&amp;q=phuket+capital&amp;stick=H4sIAAAAAAAAAOPgE-LUz9U3MMxKMk_XUsgot9JPzs_JSU0uyczP08_JT04EMYqtkhMLMksScwBjt4i2LwAAAA&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjQxY6Dma7LAhUBV2MKHdPEBmAQ6BMImAEoADAW\"><strong>Capital</strong></a><strong>: </strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?biw=1920&amp;bih=985&amp;q=Phuket+Thailand&amp;stick=H4sIAAAAAAAAAOPgE-LUz9U3MMxKMk9XAjPT4osM47UUMsqt9JPzc3JSk0sy8_P0c_KTE0GMYqvkxILMksQcAEAVCsk6AAAA&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjQxY6Dma7LAhUBV2MKHdPEBmAQmxMImQEoATAW\">Phuket</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?biw=1920&amp;bih=985&amp;q=phuket+population&amp;stick=H4sIAAAAAAAAAOPgE-LUz9U3MMxKMk_X0spOttLPyU9OLMnMz9MvLgHSxSWZyYk58UWp6UAhq4L8gtIcsCwAZYo8RDkAAAA&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjQxY6Dma7LAhUBV2MKHdPEBmAQ6BMInAEoADAX\"><strong>Population</strong></a><strong>: </strong>600,000 (2014)</p></li></ul><p></p><p><img src=\"http://res.cloudinary.com/dlvkhiu0c/image/upload/c_scale,w_1241/v1457340713/phuket_wm3owm.jpg\" alt=\"phuket\" title=\"phuket\"></p>")

